      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/i/e5b9ba/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2025-02-16T15:49:17.522Z",
      "cooked": "<p>I use Garmin Fenix 6 <strong>HR broadcasting</strong> feature to show my HR in Trainer day (ANT+ HR strap \u2192 watch \u2192 app). The issue is that during the workout the app loses the connection with the watch every now and then and I need to enable the HR broadcasting again in the watch so that the app reconnect to it again.</p>\n<p>This has been happening for a while but I wasn\u2019t sure what was the culprit: the Android phone, TrainerDay or the watch. It seems is the app, I have a new phone and I still have the problem. Also, when I use broadcasting HR with the Wahoo app, it works very well.</p>\n<p>Thanks.</p>",
