      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/forums.trainerday.com/alex/{size}/1331_2.png",
      "created_at": "2025-02-16T16:17:00.986Z",
      "cooked": "<p>One other user had issues with the garmin broadcast feature dropping out and then later he said one of updates seemed to fix it for him.  I don\u2019t see me to have this problem.  I think part of the problem stems from the fact that our app does not always reconnect quickly and we are working to fix this.</p>\n<p>I don\u2019t usually test Android much but I can test this HRM&gt;Watch&gt;TD Android in the next day or so and see if I can replicate it.  How long does it usually take before it disconnects?  Maybe I have just not tested long enough.</p>",
